            <p>The process to install Directory Lister is simple:</p>
            
            <ol>
                <li>Download and extract directory lister</li>
                <li>Upload index.php and the resources folder to your server in the folder you want listed</li>
                <li>Upload additional files to the same directory as index.php</li>
                <li>Use your web browser to navigate to the URL for the directory</li>
            </ol>

            <p>That's it! You should now see a listing of the contents of that directory.</p>
